h2. Feature 1: Environment Promotion {status:colour=Green|title=SHIPPED}

{info:title=Status: Implemented}
This feature has been built and deployed. Test cases can be promoted from DEV -> QA -> UAT -> PROD with config template references.
{info}

h3. Promotion Flow

{panel:borderColor=#7c3aed|bgColor=#faf5ff}
|| DEV || -> || QA || -> || UAT || -> || PROD ||
| AI authors + tests | | deterministic replay | | deterministic replay | | deterministic replay |
{panel}

h3. What Was Built

|| # || Item || Status ||
| 1 | *\{service.KEY\} Config References* — Agent generates plan steps with template references instead of hardcoded URLs. Post-processed automatically. | {status:colour=Green|title=Done} |
| 2 | *promote_test_case Lambda Action* — Copies test case to target env, strips resolved values, promotes config keys with empty values. | {status:colour=Green|title=Done} |
| 3 | *Sequential Promotion* — DEV -> QA only, QA -> UAT only, UAT -> PROD only. No skipping. | {status:colour=Green|title=Done} |
| 4 | *Pipeline Badge on Inventory* — Inline D -> Q -> U -> P badge on each test case. Clickable orange circle to promote. | {status:colour=Green|title=Done} |
| 5 | *Config Key Promotion* — Service config keys copied to target env DynamoDB with empty values for admin to fill. | {status:colour=Green|title=Done} |
| 6 | *Replay Script Templatization* — Frontend replaces config values with \{service.KEY\} before saving replay script. | {status:colour=Yellow|title=In Progress} |
| 7 | *Full Service Config Loading* — Agent page loads all configs from DynamoDB at startup, passes to agent. | {status:colour=Green|title=Done} |

h3. Data Model Changes

|| Field || Type || Description || Status ||
| promoted_to | TEXT[] | Array of envs promoted to | {status:colour=Green|title=Added} |
| promoted_from_env | TEXT | Source environment | {status:colour=Green|title=Added} |
| promoted_from_id | TEXT | Source test case ID | {status:colour=Green|title=Added} |
| promoted_by | TEXT | User who approved | {status:colour=Green|title=Added} |
| promoted_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | When promotion happened | {status:colour=Green|title=Added} |

