h2. Feature 2: Database Evaluation

|| Criteria || Aurora Serverless v2 || DynamoDB || Hybrid (Current) ||
| Cold start | {status:colour=Red|title=25-30s} | {status:colour=Green|title=0ms} | Depends on store |
| Cost (idle) | $0.50/mo | $0/mo | ~$0.25/mo |
| Semantic search | {status:colour=Green|title=Native pgvector} | {status:colour=Red|title=Not supported} | Aurora for search |
| Complex queries | {status:colour=Green|title=Full SQL} | {status:colour=Yellow|title=Limited} | SQL for reports |
| Multi-region | Global DB (~$50/mo) | {status:colour=Green|title=Global Tables} | Mix of both |

{note:title=Recommendation}
*Keep Hybrid — Optimize Aurora.* Fix cold start with CloudWatch canary during business hours.
{note}

