h2. Feature 5: Tagging & Test Suites

h3. Tag Types

|| Type || Examples || Purpose ||
| Suite | regression, smoke, deployment, sanity, e2e | Batch execution |
| Priority | P1-critical, P2-high, P3-medium, P4-low | Execution order |
| Feature | login, checkout, payments, profile | Map to product |
| Custom | Free-form team-defined | Flexible org |

h3. Implementation

* {{tags TEXT[]}} column with GIN index: {{WHERE tags @> ARRAY['regression']}}
* Tag chips on each test case in Inventory
* *"Run Suite"* button — select a tag, queues all matching tests
* New {{suite_runs}} table: suite_id, tag, env, team, total, passed, failed, timestamps

