h2. Feature 6: Headless Suite Execution + Smart Retry

h3. Execution Flow

{panel:borderColor=#16a34a|bgColor=#f0fdf4}
|| Trigger Suite || -> || Queue Tests || -> || Headless Replay || -> || Results || -> || Failures || -> || LLM Analyze || -> || Smart Retry || -> || Email ||
| tag: regression | | 12 tests | | no noVNC, no Xvfb | | 10 PASS | | 2 FAIL | | root cause | | adjusted approach | | if still fails |
{panel}

h3. Why Headless?

* *2-3x faster* — no Xvfb, no noVNC overhead
* *50% less memory* — 1 vCPU / 2GB (from 2 vCPU / 4GB)
* Enables *parallel execution* across multiple ECS tasks

h3. Smart Retry

|| Step || Action ||
| 1. Capture | Screenshot + DOM + console logs + network errors |
| 2. Analyze | Claude: flaky test or real bug? |
| 3. Retry | If flaky: retry with added waits / alternate selectors |
| 4. Escalate | If retry fails: email via SES with screenshot + analysis + link |

{note:title=Key Constraint}
Smart retry modifies *how* to interact (waits, selectors), never *what* to test. Steps stay the same.
{note}

h3. Parallel Architecture

{panel}
|| UI: Run Suite || -> || Lambda Orchestrator || -> || SQS Queue || -> || N x ECS Workers || -> || Aurora || -> || LLM || -> || SES ||
| tag + env | | query by tag | | 1 msg/test | | headless replay | | results | | retry failures | | email on fail |
{panel}

h3. New AWS Services

|| Service || Purpose || Cost ||
| SQS | Test distribution queue | ~$0.40/million msgs |
| SES | Email notifications | ~$0.10/1000 emails |
| S3 | Screenshots, reports | ~$0.023/GB/mo |
| Step Functions | Orchestration (optional) | ~$0.025/1000 transitions |

----

h2. Feature 7: noVNC via ALB (VPN-Friendly)

h3. The Problem

|| Check || Current {color:#dc2626}(Blocked){color} || After ALB {color:#16a34a}(Allowed){color} ||
| Port | 6080 (non-standard) | 443 (standard HTTPS) |
| Destination | Raw IP (54.23.45.67) | Domain (novnc.prompt2test.com) |
| Encryption | ws:// unencrypted | wss:// TLS encrypted |
| Protocol | Unknown WebSocket | HTTPS WebSocket upgrade |

h3. Solution

{panel:borderColor=#1d4ed8|bgColor=#eff6ff}
|| Browser || -> || Route 53 || -> || ALB || -> || ECS Task || -> || noVNC ||
| wss:// port 443 | | novnc.prompt2test.com | | HTTPS + ACM cert | | private IP :6080 | | live stream |
{panel}

h3. Implementation & Cost

|| Task || Effort ||
| CDK: ALB + cert + DNS + target group | 1 day |
| Agent: register/deregister targets | 0.5 day |
| Frontend: update noVNC URL | 0.5 day |
| Testing | 0.5 day |
| *Total* | *~2.5 days, ~$20/mo* |

